                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Favonius Bladework"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span>, target berganti ke Karakter selanjutnya secara paksa.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/f21a21302c39df14caac1bbc0a6bef40_8135790941827639770.png",
                "id": "talent65043",
                "key": "Gale Blade",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Gale Blade"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Memulihkan 2 poin HP seluruh Karaktermu dan memanggil <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dandelion Field</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/06d120531fd7d61a928bac235bbaeed2_1694058299657832669.png",
                "id": "talent18410",
                "key": "Dandelion Breeze",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Dandelion Breeze"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tahap Selesai:</span> Mengakibatkan 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo DMG</span> dan memulihkan 1 poin HP Karakter Aktifmu.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 3</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/15/25750596/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_3725717275661260414.png",
                "id": "talent78272",
                "key": "Dandelion Field",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/15/25750596/9138f4f0e38e85d3c4e035bdf2025636_9159669990349640115.png",
                "talent_imgs": [
                  {
                    "description": "",
                    "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/15/25750596/9138f4f0e38e85d3c4e035bdf2025636_9159669990349640115.png"
                  }
                ],
                "title": "Dandelion Field"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Bereaksi dengan Elemen jika sudah diberikan:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Cryo DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Hydro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Pyro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Electro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/15/25750596/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_7388727454954592098.png",
                "id": "talent31779",
                "key": "Anemo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Anemo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/03/04/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_7685720700190531397.png",
